Phase 3: Project Design Phase
System Architecture: A Multimodal "Late-Fusion" architecture where image data and text prompts are combined at the model's input layer.

Backend Logic:

input_image_setup(): Normalizes various image formats into standard byte streams.

get_gemini_response(): An orchestrated function that handles the communication with the Gemini 2.5 Flash model.

User Interface Design: A minimalist "Dashboard" style.

Top Section: Branding and file upload.

Middle Section: Real-time image preview.

Bottom Section: Dynamic Markdown report rendering.
